data.comment: The match is underway at Friends Arena.
Filip Rogic puts the ball in the net and the home team now lead 1-0.
In the minute 4, Great play from Sebastian Larsson to set up the goal.
Goteborg's Mattias Bjarsmyr has been booked in Solna.
Corner awarded to Goteborg.
In the minute 17, Goteborg have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Solna.
In Solna a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 19, Throw-in for AIK in their own half.
AIK have a goal kick.
Goal kick for AIK at Friends Arena.
In the minute 24, Free kick for Goteborg in their own half.
Can AIK get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Goteborg's half?
Free kick in a good position for AIK!
In the minute 26, AIK have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
AIK's Henok Goitom is on target but unsuccessful.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a Goteborg throw-in in AIK's half.
In the minute 28, Bartosz Grzelak is making the team's first substitution at Friends Arena with Robert Lundstrom replacing Mikael Lustig.
Throw-in for Goteborg in the half of AIK.
Corner awarded to Goteborg.
In the minute 30, In Solna, Mattias Bjarsmyr (Goteborg) misses the target with a header.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards AIK a goal kick.
It's getting dangerous! Free kick for Goteborg close to the penalty box.
In the minute 31, AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.
AIK drive forward at breakneck speed but are pulled up for offside.
Throw-in for AIK at Friends Arena.
In the minute 33, Goteborg to take a throw-in in AIK territory.
Ball goes out of play for a AIK goal kick.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Goteborg in their own half.
In the minute 36, At Friends Arena, Goteborg are penalized for being offside.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards the home team a throw-in.
Corner awarded to Goteborg.
In the minute 38, Ball safe as AIK is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to AIK.
Free kick for Goteborg in the half of AIK.
In the minute 42, Goteborg have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
AIK awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
In the minute 44, Throw-in AIK.
Free kick Goteborg.
In the minute 45, 1 minutes will be added to the 1st half.
AIK have a goal kick.
The first-half has come to a close in Solna.
Filip Rogic (AIK) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
In the minute 46, The whistle has gone to start the second-half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
AIK have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
In the minute 49, A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Play has been interrupted briefly in Solna to check on Alexander Jallow, who is grimacing with pain.
Erik Ring is down and play has been interrupted for a few moments.
In the minute 51, Alexander Jallow for Goteborg is back on the field again.
AIK's Erik Ring is back in action after a slight knock.
AIK push upfield and Henok Goitom gets his head to the ball. The attempt is cleared by an alert Goteborg defence.
In the minute 53, Ball safe as AIK is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards the home team a throw-in.
Goteborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 55, In Solna, Giorgi Kharaishvili of Goteborg is presented with a shooting opportunity. But the strike is blocked by the covering defence.
Corner awarded to Goteborg.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards AIK a goal kick.
In the minute 58, Goteborg awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to AIK.
The match has been stopped briefly for attention to the injured Erik Ring.
In the minute 60, In Solna AIK attack through Robert Lundstrom. The finish is off target, however.
Goal kick for Goteborg at Friends Arena.
Erik Ring is back on the pitch.
In the minute 61, Henok Goitom puts the ball in the net and the home team extend their lead. The score-line now reads 2-0.
Eric Kahl with an assist there.
Throw-in for Goteborg in the half of AIK.
In the minute 63, AIK needs to be cautious. Goteborg have an attacking throw-in.
Goteborg to take a throw-in in AIK territory.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a throw-in for Goteborg, close to AIK's area.
In the minute 64, Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
Throw-in for Goteborg at Friends Arena.
In the minute 66, Corner awarded to Goteborg.
Ferran Sibila Pont (Goteborg) is making a first substitution, with Alexander Farnerud replacing Jakob Johansson.
Throw-in Goteborg.
Can Goteborg capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
In the minute 69, Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a Goteborg throw-in in AIK's half.
Ball goes out of play for a AIK goal kick.
In the minute 71, Free kick for AIK in the half of Goteborg.
Erik Ring (AIK) does not seem to be able to continue. He is replaced by Erick Otieno.
Throw-in for AIK in their own half.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
In the minute 73, Free kick AIK.
AIK have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Throw-in for AIK at Friends Arena.
In the minute 76, Goteborg are coming forward and Giorgi Kharaishvili gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Solna.
The away team replace Mattias Bjarsmyr with Robin Soder.
In the minute 77, Emil Holm is on a sub for Pontus Wernbloom for Goteborg.
The away team have replaced Yahya Kalley with Andre Calisir. This is the fourth substitution made today by Ferran Sibila Pont.
Throw-in high up the field for AIK in Solna.
In the minute 79, Goteborg have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards the home team a throw-in.
Corner awarded to AIK.
In the minute 81, A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Goteborg's Alexander Jallow gets in a shot on goal at Friends Arena. But the effort is unsuccessful.
Can Goteborg capitalize from this throw-in deep inside AIK's half?
In the minute 84, Can Goteborg get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in AIK's half?
AIK advance rapidly upfield but Mohammed Al-Hakim blows for offside.
Patrik Karlsson Lagemyr of Goteborg gets in a strike, but is off target.
In the minute 86, It's a goal kick for the home team in Solna.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Goteborg just outside AIK's area.
In the minute 87, In Solna a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Erick Otieno (AIK) has received a yellow card from Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Tobias Sana (Goteborg) has received a first yellow card.
Mohammed Al-Hakim waits before resuming play because Budimir Janosevic for AIK is still down.
In the minute 89, AIK's Budimir Janosevic looks ok and returns to the pitch.
Ball goes out of play for a Goteborg goal kick.
AIK have a dangerous throw-in.
Throw-in for Goteborg in their own half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim will wait an extra 6 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 2nd half.
Goal kick for AIK at Friends Arena.
Enock Kofi Adu for AIK drives towards goal at Friends Arena. But the finish is unsuccessful.
AIK have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Goteborg awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
Throw-in Goteborg.
Goteborg have a goal kick.
The match has come to a close in Solna. The final score is 2-0.
Kolbeinn Sigthorsson is replacing Paulos Abraham for the home team.
At Friends Arena, August Erlingmark has been yellow-carded for the away team.
